g chopped mixture in mixing bowl and sauté without measuring cup <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add reserved steamed millet, salt and pepper and mix with aid of spatula <b>10 sec\/\/speed 4<b>. Adjust seasoning to taste. Place 2-3 tbsp of stuffing on each steamed cabbage leaf and roll up. Place rolls in Varoma dish and tray, making sure overlapping ends of cabbage leaves are tucked under the rolls."},{"content":"Place 500 g reserved cooking liquid in mixing bowl, set Varoma in position and steam <b>30 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set covered Varoma aside on a plate to keep warm. Empty cooking liquid into a jug and set aside this second cooking liquid for the mushroom sauce."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Sauce"},{"content":"Place butter and reserved chopped onion-garlic-mushroom mixture in mixing bowl and sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add cream and 200 g of the reserved second cooking liquid and cook <b>5 min\/98°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add salt and pepper and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 9<b>, then adjust seasoning to taste. Serve stuffed cabbage rolls hot, drizzled with mushroom sauce."}],"basicInfo":["medium","40m","1h 40m","6 portions"]}